Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly, Twilight, for helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Big Macintosh I could get all these\NGolden Delicious in the barn by lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, he's gonna walk down Stirrup\NStreet in one of Granny's girdles, heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem at all, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad, the goal is lunchtime.\NAll this hard work is making me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really, Spike? You've been lounging\Non my back all morning while we worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! You two were taking\Nso long, I missed snacktime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess be better get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope... worm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike! That looks delicious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from Princess Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear ye, hear ye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Grand Royal Highness\NPrincess Celestia of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...is pleased to announce\Nthe Grand Galloping Gala...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be held in the magnificent capital\Ncity of Canterlot on the 21st day of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...yadda yadda yadda...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...cordially extends an invitation\Nto Twilight Sparkle plus one guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Galloping Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Galloping Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Two tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, great! I've never been to the Gala.\NHave you, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No and I plan to keep it that way. I don't\Nwant any of that girly frilly frou-frou nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on Spike! A dance would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice?! It's a hiccup more than just nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Land sakes! If I had an apple stand set up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...ponies would be chewin' our tasty\Nvittles till the cows came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much business\NI could drum up for Sweet Apple Acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, with all that money we could\Ndo a heap of fixin' up round here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We could replace that saggy old roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And Big Macintosh could\Nreplace that saggy old plow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And Granny Smith could\Nreplace that saggy old hip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I'd give my left hind\Nleg to go to that Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, in that case, would you like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we talking about the Grand Galloping Gala?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash. You told me you were\Ntoo busy to help me harvest apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you busy doin'? Spyin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I was busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just happened to hear\Nthat you have an extra ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, but...\N-Yes! This is so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts perform at the Grand Galloping\NGala every year. I can see it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will be watching the sky.\NTheir eyes riveted on the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, in would fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I would draw their attention\Nwith my Super Speed Strut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would mesmerize them\Nwith my Fantastic Filly Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And for my grand finale the Buccaneer Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The ponies would go wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts would insist that my signature\Nmoves be incorporated into their routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And then welcome me as their newest member.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see, Twilight? This could be\Nmy one chance to show 'em my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on just one pony pickin' minute here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for that ticket first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So? That doesn't mean you own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Well, I challenge you to\Na hoof wrestle. Winner gets the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! These are MY tickets!\NI'll decide who gets it, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever has the best reason to go,\Nshould get the ticket, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Drummin' up business for the farm?\N-A chance to audition for the Wonderbolts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Money to fix Granny's hip!\N-Living the dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Those are all pretty\Ngood reasons, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to that. I am starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you, but I can't make\Nimportant decisions on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll think about it over lunch\Nand get back to you two. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So who you're gonna give the ticket to, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike. But I really\Ncan't think straight when I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So where should we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bats! Bats on my face! HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! These aren't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickets to the Grand Galloping Gala?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most amazing incredible tremendous\Nsuper-fun wonderful terrifically humongous\Nparty in all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always always ALWAYS wanted to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, the Grand Galloping Gala\Nis the best place for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, the Grand Galloping Gala\Nis the best place for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hip hip hurray,\Nit's the best place for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For Pinkie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With decorations and streamers and fairy lights\Nand pinwheels and pi√±atas and pincushions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With goodies like sugar cubes and sugar canes\Nand sundaes and sunbeams and sasparilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get to play my favoritest of favorite\Nfantabulous games like pin the tail on the pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, the Grand Galloping Gala\Nis the best place for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, the Grand Galloping Gala\Nis the best place for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cause it's the most gallerific\Nsuperly-teriffic gala ever in the whole Galaxy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh thank you, Twilight!\NIt's the most wonderfulest gift ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these what I think they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, YES! Twilight's taking my to\Nthe Grand Galloping Gala in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I design ensembles for the Gala every year,\Nbut I've never had the opportunity to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the society, the culture, the glamor!\NIt's where I truly belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And where I'm destined to meet... HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would stroll through the Gala\Nand everyone would wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is that mysterious mare?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They would never guess that I was just\Na simple pony from little old Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I would cause such a sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I would be invited for an\Naudience with Princess Celestia herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Princess would be so taken\Nwith the style and elegance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...that she would introduce me to HIM!\NHer nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The most handsome, eligible\Nunicorn stallion in Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Our eyes would meet, our hearts would melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our courtship would be magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He would ask for my hoof in marriage\Nand of course I would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have a royal wedding,\Nbefitting a princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...which is what I would\Nbecome upon marrying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The stallion of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! I simply cannot believe you would\Ninvite Pinkie Pie, so she could party...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and prevent me from meeting my true love!\NHow could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel! These are perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen guys, I haven't decided\Nwho to give the extra ticket to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, I would just like to ask...\NI mean, if it would be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you haven't given it to someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You?! You want to go to the Gala?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... yes. Or actually, kind of. You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so much the Grand Galloping Gala...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...as it is the wondrous private gated\Ngarden that surrounds the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers are said the be the most\Nbeautiful and fragrant in all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For the night of the Gala and that night\Nalone will they all be in bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's just the flora!\NDon't get me started on the fauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's loons and toucans and bitterns, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hummingbirds that can really hum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And buzzards that can really buzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And blue jays and red jays and green\Njays, pink jays and pink flamingos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, Fluttershy, it sounds... beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait just a minute!\N-Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I mean, yes... I mean, maybe.\NLook, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't risk a goody four-shoes like you\Ngiving that ticket away to just anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait just another minute!\N-Applejack! Were you following me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I was following this one to make\Nsure she didn't try any funny business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Still tryin' to take my ticket.\N-YOUR ticket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But Twilight's taking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,QUIET!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then I said "Oatmeal? Are you craz..." Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! There's no use in arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Twilight...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my decision and I'm\Ngonna make it on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I certainly can't think\Nstraight with all this noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't worry, I'll figure this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Spike. What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All five of my best friends have\Nreally good reasons to go to the Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, Rainbow Dash,\NPinkie Pie or Fluttershy, Rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who should go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T DECIDE!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, he just wants to take your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I would love a daffodil and daisy sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any rubies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Okay, I'll have the hay fries. Extra crispy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we have to try another restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I like grass just fine, but would\Nit hurt anybody to offer some gemstones?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean about the Gala\Nand the ticket and who I should take!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, you're still on THAT?\N-Spike, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I choose? And when I do choose,\Nwill the other four be mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I could give up\Nmy ticket and give away two...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that would still leave three\Ndisappointed ponies. What if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you. This looks so good. I'm sure\Neverything will be much clearer once I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Madame? Are you going to\Neat your food in ze rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there, best friend forever I've ever ever had?\NEnjoying the sunny weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya mean? I just saw the smartest,\Nmost generous pony about to get rained on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I though I'd kick a hole\Nin the clouds to keep her dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...so she can dine at peace. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow. You're not trying to get extra\Nconsideration for the extra ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...by doing the extra special favors, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? No no no, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I'd do it for anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow, I am not comfortable\Naccepting unwanted favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd appreciate if you closed up\Nthat rain cloud right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Twilight! It's raining.\N-No. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me before you catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we are THE BEST OF FRIENDS,\Nare we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what the best of friends do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Makeover!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Rarity...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Oh, you're simply darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It is kinda pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you! Oh, Spike. I have a dandy\Nlittle outfit for the dashing gent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, Spike.\N-Now you just need a hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! I don't want any part of this girly\Ngala gunk. See you back at the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who needs him anyway?\NThis is all about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And how fabulous you'll look\Nat the Grand Galloping Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. The Grand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And, oh my goodness, what a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to have an ensemble\Nof my own that matches yours to a tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be the belles of the ball, you and I.\NEveryone would be clamoring for our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All eyes would be on us. And then everyone\Nwould finally know, the most beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...most talented, most sophisticated\Npony in all of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...is Rarity the Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And Twilight Sparkle, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what's going on. You're just\Nbuttering me up so I give you the extra ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to wait for my\Ndecision just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me, I've been\Ntrying all day just to get some lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did somepony say lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got apple pie, apple fritters, apple tarts,\Napple dumplings, apple crisps, apple crumbles...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...aaand apple Brown Betty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The dessert. Not my auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd ya say there, best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who I'm giving the ticket to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And all these favors aren't\Nmaking it any easier to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm less sure now\Nthan I was this morning! Aaargh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So... that's a maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought being showered with\Nfavors would be so aggravating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Not you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Well, hello, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind but we're all\Ndoing a little spring cleaning for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well... better late than never, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Angel's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not doing this for the ticket, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'm doing this because you're\Nmy very best friend! Right, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We are just doing this for the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No no NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is all very nice of you and Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm not accepting any extra favors\Nuntil I've made my final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to have to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twilight is my bestest friend, whoopee! Whoopee!{\i0}\N-Pinkie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the cutest, smartest, all-around best pony! Pony!{\i0}\N-Pinkie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet if I throw a super-duper fun party! Party!{\i0}\N-Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll give her extra ticket to the Gala to meee!{\i0}\N-PINKIEEE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,At least the other ponies *try*\Nto be subtle about the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait... What ticket? What gala?\N-Oh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight has an extra ticket\Nto the Grand Galloping Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,THE GRAND GALLOPING GALA?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I ever told you how much\NI love your mane?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wash your dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Would you like any help with your gardening?\N-I have a cartload of extra carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... gonna... RUUUUN!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Warn me next time you're gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know it was gonna happen!\NNot quick, lock the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't decide, I just can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to all of you and I just\Ncan't stand to disappoint any of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...and giving me gifts and doing me\Nfavors won't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're all my friends and I wanna\Nmake you all happy and I can't! I JUST CAN'T!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, sugar... I didn't mean to\Nput so much pressure on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it helps, I don't want the ticket anymore.\NYou can give it to somepony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't feel bad, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. I feel just awful\Nthat I made you feel so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And me too. It's no fun upsetting your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, it was unfair of me\Nto try to force you as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,YES! That means, the ticket is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the ticket, I've got the ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... I haven't perfected my signature\Nmoves for the Wonderbolts anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need that ticket either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We all got so gung-ho about\Ngoing to the Gala...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...that we couldn't see how\Nungung-ho we were makin' you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, take down a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Princess Celestia. I've learned that one of\Nthe joys of friendship is sharing your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it's not enough\Nblessings to go around...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...having more than your friends\Ncan make you feel pretty awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, though I appreciate the invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will be returning both tickets\Nto the Grand Galloping Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If my friends can't all go,\NI don't wanna go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you don't have to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I've made up my mind.\NSpike, you can send the letter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you won't get to go to the Gala either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, girls. I couldn't possibly enjoy\Nmyself without my best friends there with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd rather not go at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, wallop my withers, Spike. Isn't that just like\Na boy. Can't handle the least bit of sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah, Nelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from the Princess? That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My faithful student Twilight.\NWhy didn't you just say so in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Six tickets to the Grand Galloping Gala!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow us to treat you to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great way to apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And to celebrate! Come on, everyone!\NThe cupcakes are on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How come I don't get a ticket to the Gala?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And one for you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... gross! I have to go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
